<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>New Round</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/newroundstyles.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Kumbh+Sans:wght@100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body>
   <div id="headerLinks">
          <form action="/about" method="GET">
              <button style="color: grey; border: none; font-family: Lemon Milk; font-size: 1rem; background-color: transparent">about</button>
          </form>
          <p style="font-size: 25px; font-weight: 700; margin-top:22px; color: #b30000; height: 100%; margin-left: 19px"><a  onclick="homefunc()"><img src="/images/logo.svg" style="height: 100%"></a></p>
          <form action="/profile" method="GET">
              <button style="color: grey; border: none; font-family: Lemon Milk; font-size: 1rem; background-color: transparent">profiles</button>
          </form>
    </div>
    <div id="topSpaceFill"></div>
    <div id="content">
        <h2 style="margin-top: 0; text-align: center">Current Military Power</h2>
        <table id="statsTable">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Nation</th>
                    <th>Army</th>
                    <th>Navy</th>
                    <th>Morale</th>
                    <th>Total</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <% for (let i = 0; i < stillIn.length; i++) { %>
                    <tr>
                        <td><%=stillIn[i].name%></td>
                        <td><%=stillIn[i].army%></td>
                        <td><%=stillIn[i].navy%></td>
                        <td><%=stillIn[i].moral%></td>
                        <td><%=stillIn[i].total%></td>
                    </tr>
                <% } %>
                <!-- Add more rows as needed -->
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <h4><span style="color: #b30000">Eliminated countries: </span>
<% if (eliminated.length === 1) { %>
    <%= eliminated[0].name %>
<% } else { %>
    <% for (let t = 0; t < eliminated.length; t++) { %>
        <%= eliminated[t].name %><% if (t < eliminated.length - 1) { %>,<% } %>
    <% } %>
<% } %></h4>
        <form style="flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column" action="/combatants" method="POST">
            <div id="paraSelect">
            
                <p id="summary" style="flex: 1; font-family: Kumbh Sans; font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 0"><span style="font-weight: 600">This is the current distribution of points.</span> Power shifts and alliance loyalties have changed the world scene, casting a shadow of uncertainty over global affairs. Tensions are high. The geopolitical scene hums with anticipation. <%= topCountries[0].name%> and <%= topCountries[1].name%> are the most powerful nations, while <%=lowCountry[0].name%> is at the bottom. Who will find themselves at war next? You decide...</p>
            
                <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #d5dede 49.8%, black, #d5dede 50.2%); flex: 1">
                    <div style="flex: 1">
                        <h3 style="margin-top: 0">Belligerent 1</h3>
                        <select name="option1">
                            <% for (let n = 0; n < stillIn.length; n++) { %>
                                <option name="dropOp"><%=stillIn[n].name%></option>
                            <% } %>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin: auto;">
                        <p id="versus">V.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div style="flex: 1; text-align: end">
                        <h3 style="margin-top: 0">Belligerent 2</h3>
                        <select name="option2">
                            <% for (let n = 0; n < stillIn.length; n++) { %>
                                <option><%=stillIn[n].name%></option>
                            <% } %>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
<!--                <div style="flex-grow: 1"></div>-->
                
            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 30px">
                    <a style="text-decoration: none" class="button" href="javascript:history.go(-1)">&larr;</a>
                    <button class="button" type="submit">&rarr;</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    
    
    
    <script>
        async function homefunc() { //search box function
            window.location.href = '/'; 
        }
    </script>
</body>
    <footer id="footerDiv">
        <p>World War I Game Â© 2024 M. Felsmann</p>
    </footer>
</html>
